    "description": "Magmag, Inc. engages in the development and operation of content distribution platform in Japan. It operates through Platform, Media Advertising, and Others segments. The company operates MagMag!, an email newsletter distribution platform; MagOne, a fan site platform; MAG2NEWS, which provides news analysis and column articles in the fields of politics, economics, business, entertainment, science, and others; MONEY VOICE, an economic media site that provides information for investors on stocks, foreign exchange, bonds, futures, real estate, and others; TRIP EDITOR, a travel web media outlet; and by them, a love web media service, as well as MagMag Reader App, which allows users to view email newsletter content through an app. It is also involved in the planning, development, and operation of Internet media; operation and sale of advertising space to be placed in web media and email newsletters; and event planning and management activities. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Shinagawa, Japan. Magmag, Inc. is a subsidiary of AirTrip Corp."
